{"tid":1533071,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一句講哂 五大訴求比四樣你係冇真普選 受唔受","createTime":"2019-09-02T16:07:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T17:18:21.000Z","uid":14159,"like":30,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"0c6dc0313231e6b265026addc6d60119f8f9685b","tid":1533071,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:07:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">警世</div></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">一定唔可以受!!!</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家一定要時刻保持醒覺!<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可唔係齋講<br />\n<br />\n一、全面撤回逃犯條例修訂草案<br />\n二、根據香港法例第86章成立有法律約束力的獨立調查委員會<br />\n三、收回六一二暴動定性<br />\n四、撤銷對「反送中」抗爭者的無理控罪<br />\n五、落實真普選<br />\n<br />\n唔知道路透今日流出來ge錄音係有咩居心 我地要繼續堅持五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n唔止緊記五大訴求 要同你地身邊ge淺黃中立講 感染佢地<br />\n唔好睇少淺黃同中立 佢地係二百萬人入面ge其中一批<br />\n冇佢地ge支持我地都唔會再走得幾遠<br />\n<br />\n所以要提醒佢地<br />\n所有野都係一定要 缺一不可<br />\n尤其係真普選<br />\n真普選係一切問題ge根源之一 冇真普選只會有另一個林鄭出來害人<br />\n<br />\n只要一日五大訴求未被滿足 一日抗爭都要繼續<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">時刻銘記每一個烈士 <br />\n我地答應左的話<br />\n佢地係唔會原諒我地架</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DnDpoUw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDnDpoUw.jpg&h=8a4507ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3e325ed59d526d46b65e4c65be72468b6d4fb97c","tid":1533071,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:08:08.000Z","msg":"pish 1/10"},{"pid":"dd3cfd919344d15fc7185a425c194618861ab271","tid":1533071,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:08:53.000Z","msg":"pish 2/10"},{"pid":"a5ec0089b4667950e7453e5c86c02083f28c609c","tid":1533071,"uid":14159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T16:09:15.000Z","msg":"pish 3/10"},{"pid":"bb6ed21904b382d713c167464717ef4225bb7937","tid":1533071,"uid":8232,